        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Veterans Flexibility of Annuities for Income Relief Act of 2018 or the Veterans FAIR Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill expands the circumstances&nbsp;under which&nbsp;an individual may opt out of the Survivor Benefits Plan for veterans, including by extending the opt-out window from one year to six years.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
